\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{d^{2}\psi}{dx^{2}}+\frac{2m}{\hslash^{2}}(E-V)\psi=0
\]

\end_inset

经整理可得
\begin_inset Formula $u(x)$
\end_inset

满足的方程: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\frac{d^{2}u}{dx^{2}}+2ik\frac{du}{dx}+\left[\frac{2m}{\hslash^{2}}(E-V)-k^{2}\right]u=0\label{eq:10-60}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

在势场突变的点, 波函数及其导数
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{d\psi}{dx}=e^{ikx}\frac{du}{dx}+ike^{ikx}u
\]

\end_inset

必须连续。因为
\begin_inset Formula $e^{ikx}$
\end_inset

是连续函数, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(x)$
\end_inset

及
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{d\psi(x)}{dx}$
\end_inset

