i(\alpha-k)e^{i(\alpha-k)c}A_{0}-i(\alpha+k)e^{-i(\alpha+k)c}B_{0}=(\beta-ik)e^{-(\beta-ik)b}C_{0}-(\beta+ik)e^{(\beta+ik)b}D_{0}\label{eq:10-74}
