\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

是实数, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-1\leqslant\cos(ka)\leqslant1
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-1\leqslant\frac{\beta^{2}-\alpha^{2}}{2\alpha\beta}\sinh(\beta b)\sin(\alpha c)+\cosh(\beta b)\cos(\alpha c)\leqslant1
\]

\end_inset

