\begin_inset Formula $V_{0}b$
\end_inset

保持有限值。令
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim\frac{\beta^{2}ab}{2}=P,\beta b=\sqrt{\frac{2Pb}{a}}\ll1
\]

\end_inset

利用上式并把 
\begin_inset Formula $e^{\beta b}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $e^{-\beta b}$
\end_inset

