\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中求和不包括
\begin_inset Formula $n=0$
\end_inset

的项, 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{0}$
\end_inset

是势能的平均值。势能是实数,  有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V(x)=V^{*}(x)
\]

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V_{0}+\sum_{n}V_{n}e^{i\frac{2\pi}{a}nx}=V_{0}^{*}+\sum_{n}V_{n}^{*}e^{-i\frac{2\pi}{a}nx}
\]

\end_inset

