\begin_layout Standard
按照微扰理论,  Hamilton 算符应写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{H}=\hat{H}_{0}+\hat{H}'
\]

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{H}_{0}=-\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\frac{d^{2}}{dx^{2}}+V_{0}
\]

\end_inset

一般选取
\begin_inset Formula $V_{0}=0$
\end_inset

作为能量零点。零级方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\hat{H}_{0}\psi_{k}^{0}=E_{k}^{0}\psi_{k}^{0}
\]

\end_inset

的本征值为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{k}^{0}=\frac{\hslash^{2}k^{2}}{2m}
\]

\end_inset

相应的归一化波函数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{k}^{0}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{L}}e^{ikx}
\]

\end_inset

设晶体有
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

个原胞, 线度为
\begin_inset Formula $L=Na$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

是晶格的周期, 即平移基矢的长度。而
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\hat{H}'=\sum_{n}V_{n}e^{i\frac{2\pi}{a}nx}\label{eq:10-80}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

代表势能偏离平均值的部分, 它随坐标变化, 并被看作为微扰势。电子的能量可写成为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{k}=E_{k}^{0}+E_{k}^{(1)}+E_{k}^{(2)}+\cdots
\]

\end_inset

一级微扰能量
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
E_{k}^{(1)} & =\int_{0}^{L}\psi_{k}^{0*}(x)\left[\sum_{n}V_{n}e^{i\frac{2\pi}{a}nx}\right]\psi_{k}^{0}(x)dx=\int_{0}^{L}\left|\psi_{k}^{0}(x)\right|^{2}\left[V(x)-V_{0}\right]dx\\
 & =\int_{0}^{L}\left|\psi_{k}^{0}(x)\right|^{2}V(x)dx-V_{0}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

其中第一项, 按定义就等于势能的平均值
\begin_inset Formula $V_{0}$
\end_inset

, 因此
