式中求和不包括
\begin_inset Formula $k'=k$
\end_inset

项, 而微扰矩阵元
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
H_{kk'}'=\int_{0}^{L}\psi_{k}^{0*}\hat{H}'\psi_{k'}^{0}dx=\int_{0}^{L}\psi_{k}^{0*}\left[V(x)-V_{0}\right]\psi_{k'}^{0}dx=\int_{0}^{L}\psi_{k}^{0*}V(x)\psi_{k'}^{0}dx
\]

