\end_inset

的正交关系。上式按原胞划分可写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
H_{kk'}'=\frac{1}{L}\int_{0}^{L}e^{i\left(k'-k\right)n}V(x)dx=\frac{1}{Na}\sum_{n=0}^{N-1}\int_{na}^{(n+1)a}e^{i\left(k'-k\right)n}V(x)dx
\]

\end_inset

对不同的原胞
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

, 引入积分变数
\begin_inset Formula $\xi$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x=\xi+na
\]

\end_inset

并考虑到
\begin_inset Formula $V(x)$
\end_inset

的周期性: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V(\xi+na)=V(\xi)
\]

\end_inset

于是
\begin_inset Formula $H_{kk'}'$
\end_inset

, 可写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
H_{kk'}'=\frac{1}{Na}\sum_{n=0}^{N-1}e^{i\left(k'-k\right)na}\int_{0}^{a}e^{i\left(k'-k\right)\xi}V(\xi)d\xi=\left[\frac{1}{a}\int_{0}^{a}e^{i\left(k'-k\right)\xi}V(\xi)d\xi\right]\frac{1}{N}\sum_{n=0}^{N-1}\left[e^{i\left(k'-k\right)a}\right]^{n}
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $k-k'=2\pi n/a$
\end_inset

时,  则上式求和中的每一项均为1, 故
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{N}\sum_{n=0}^{N-1}\left[e^{i\left(k'-k\right)a}\right]^{n}=1
\]

\end_inset

