E_{k}=\frac{\hslash^{2}k^{2}}{2m}+\sum_{n}\frac{2m\left|V_{n}\right|^{2}}{\hslash^{2}k^{2}-\hslash^{2}\left(k-\frac{2\pi n}{a}\right)^{2}}\label{eq:10-82}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

