\begin_layout Standard
在周期势场
\begin_inset Formula $V(x)$
\end_inset

作用下, 电子的波函数为Bloch 波
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{k}(x)=e^{ikx}u_{k}(x)
\]

\end_inset

由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-60"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式知, 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{k}(x)$
\end_inset

所满足的方程为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\left[\frac{d^{2}}{dx^{2}}+2ik\frac{d}{dx}-k^{2}\right]u_{k}(x)+V(x)u_{k}(x)=E(k)u_{k}(x)\label{eq:10-97}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当波矢小于零时, 波函数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{-k}(x)=e^{-ikx}u_{-k}(x)
\]

\end_inset

其本征值为
\begin_inset Formula $E(-k)$
\end_inset

, 由(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-97"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式知, 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{-k}(x)$
\end_inset

应满足方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\left[\frac{d^{2}}{dx^{2}}-2ik\frac{d}{dx}-k^{2}\right]u_{-k}(x)+V(x)u_{-k}(x)=E(-k)u_{-k}(x)
\]

\end_inset

对(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-97"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式取复数共轭, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\left[\frac{d^{2}}{dx^{2}}-2ik\frac{d}{dx}-k^{2}\right]u_{k}^{*}(x)+V(x)u_{k}^{*}(x)=E(k)u_{k}^{*}(x)
\]

\end_inset

比较以上两个方程, 可以得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
E(k)= & E(-k)\label{eq:10-98}\\
u_{k}^{*}(x)= & u_{-k}(x)\label{eq:10-99}
\end{align}

\end_inset

为了明确起见, 常把(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-98"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式记为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E_{s}(k_{x})=E_{s}(-k_{x})
\]

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

是能带序数, 
\begin_inset Formula $k_{x}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

方向的波矢。上式表明,  
\begin_inset Formula $E_{s}$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $k_{x}$
\end_inset

的偶函数, 而速度
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v_{x}=\frac{1}{\hslash}\frac{dE_{S}(k_{x})}{dk_{x}}
\]

\end_inset

则是
\begin_inset Formula $k_{x}$
\end_inset

的奇函数, 即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
v_{x}(-k_{x})=-v_{x}(k_{x})\label{eq:10-100}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

上式表明, 在波矢为
\begin_inset Formula $k_{x}$
\end_inset

