\begin_layout Section
紧束缚近似—— LCAO 法计算能带
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
固体能带的计算是一个比较复杂的问题, 并有多种计算能带的方法。本节只讨论其中的一种: 紧束缚近似——LCAO法。紧束缚近似的出发点是, 电子在一个原子附近时,
 将主要受到该原子场的作用, 而把其它原子场的作用看成是微扰。由此可以得到电子在原子中的能级与在晶休中的能带之间的相互关系。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
模型与微扰计算
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果完全不考虑原子之间的相互影响, 那么在某格点
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boldsymbol{R}_{m}=m_{1}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+m_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{2}+m_{3}\boldsymbol{a}_{3}
\]

\end_inset

附近的一个电子将以原子束缚态(原子轨道)
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

的形式环绕
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{m}$
\end_inset

点运动。这里假定是简单晶格, 每个原胞中只含一个原子。显然
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

 满足孤立原子的单电子波动方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left[-\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\nabla^{2}+V\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\right]\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)=\epsilon_{i}\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\label{eq:10-123}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula $V\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

为
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{m}$
\end_inset

格点的原子势场, 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon_{i}$
\end_inset

为其原子单电子能级。晶体中单电子的波动方程为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left[-\frac{\hslash^{2}}{2m}\nabla^{2}+U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)\right]\psi\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)=E\psi\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)\label{eq:10-124}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

为周期性势场, 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

为晶体中的单电子能量(即能级), 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

是晶体中的单电子波函数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
在紧束缚近似中, 把方程(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-123"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)看作为零级近似。因为
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

是各格点原子势场之和, 而
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)-V\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

自然就是格点
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{m}$
\end_inset

以外的其它原子的势场, 对于束缚在
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{m}$
\end_inset

附近的电子说来, 可把
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)-V\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

视为微扰。设晶体中有
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

个原子(格点), 则将有
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

个波函数
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}$
\end_inset

, 它们具有相同的能量
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon_{i}$
\end_inset

, 即
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

重简并的。这实际上是把原子间的相互作用看作微扰的简并微扰法, 微扰以后的状态
\begin_inset Formula $\psi\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

是
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

个简并态的线性组合: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\psi\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)=\sum_{m}a_{m}\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\label{eq:10-125}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

把上式代入(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-124"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 并利用(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-123"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\sum_{m}a_{m}\left[\epsilon_{i}+U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)-V\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\right]\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)=E\sum_{m}a_{m}\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\label{eq:10-126}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
假定不同格点的
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}$
\end_inset

重迭很小, 即近似认为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\int\varphi_{i}^{*}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{n}\right)d\boldsymbol{r}=\delta_{mn}\label{eq:10-127}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

这个近似只是为了数学表述上的简化, 没有实质性影响。以
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}^{*}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{n}\right)$
\end_inset

左乘(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-126"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式并积分得
\family roman
\series medium
\shape up
\size normal
\emph off
\bar no
\strikeout off
\xout off
\uuline off
\uwave off
\noun off
\color none

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum_{m}a_{m}\left\{ \epsilon_{i}\delta_{mn}+\int\varphi_{i}^{*}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{n}\right)\left[U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)-V\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\right]\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)d\boldsymbol{r}\right\} =E\sum_{m}a_{m}\delta_{mn}
\]

\end_inset

化简得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\sum_{m}a_{m}\int\varphi_{i}^{*}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{n}\right)\left[U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)-V\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\right]\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)d\boldsymbol{r}=\left(E-\epsilon_{i}\right)a_{n}\label{eq:10-128}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}^{*}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{n}\right)$
\end_inset

有
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

种可能的选取方法, 上式实际上是
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

个联立方程中的一个方程。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
下面考虑(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-128"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 中的积分。令
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\xi=\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}
\]

\end_inset

并考虑
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

为周期函数, 则(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-128"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式的积分为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\int\varphi_{i}^{*}\left[\xi-\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\right]\left[U\left(\xi\right)-V\left(\xi\right)\right]\varphi_{i}\left(\xi\right)d\xi=-J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\label{eq:10-129}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

上式表明, 积分的结果只是相对位置
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

的函数, 因此引入符号
\begin_inset Formula $J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $U\left(\xi\right)-V\left(\xi\right)$
\end_inset

是周期场减掉在原点的原子场, 这个场仍为负值, 故上式的结果有一负号。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-129"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式代入(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-128"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-\sum_{m}a_{m}J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)=\left(E-\epsilon_{i}\right)a_{n}\label{eq:10-130}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

这是以
\begin_inset Formula $a_{m}$
\end_inset

为未知数的齐次线性方程组, 由于该方程组中的系数只由
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)$
\end_inset

 决定, 故方程有下列简单形式的解
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
a_{m}=ce^{i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{R}_{m}}\label{eq:10-131}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

为归一化因子, 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{k}$
\end_inset

为任意常数矢量, 把上式代入(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-130"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

), 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E-\epsilon_{i}=-\sum_{m}J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)e^{i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)}=-\sum_{j}J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right)e^{i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{R}_{s}}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{s}=\boldsymbol{R}_{n}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}$
\end_inset

。对于一个确定的
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{k}$
\end_inset

值, 由上式可以确定能量
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E\left(\boldsymbol{k}\right)=\epsilon_{i}-\sum_{j}J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right)e^{i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{R}_{s}}\label{eq:10-132}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

把(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-131"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式代入(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-125"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 得
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\psi_{k}\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)=c\sum_{m}e^{i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{R}_{m}}\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)\label{eq:10-133}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

式中
\begin_inset Formula $c=\frac{1}{\sqrt{N}}$
\end_inset

为归一化因子, 容易验证(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-133"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式满足归一化条件, 其中
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

表示原胞总数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-133"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式可以改写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\psi_{k}\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)=\frac{1}{\sqrt{N}}e^{i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{r}}\sum_{m}e^{-i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)}\varphi_{i}\left(\boldsymbol{r}-\boldsymbol{R}_{m}\right)
\]

\end_inset

括号内如
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{r}$
\end_inset

增加格矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{n}=n_{1}\boldsymbol{a}_{1}+n_{2}\boldsymbol{a}_{2}+n_{3}\boldsymbol{a}_{3}$
\end_inset

, 它可以直接并入
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{m}$
\end_inset

, 由于求和遍及所有格点, 结果并不改变连加式的值, 这表明括号内是一个周期函数, 因而(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-133"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式表示的
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{k}\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

是Bloch函数矢量
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{k}$
\end_inset

为简约波矢, 它的取值应限制在简约Brillouin区。在 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec:10-12"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 节中我们曾证明, 在简约Brillouin区内含有的波矢
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{k}$
\end_inset

的数目为
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

, 所以总共可得到
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

个如(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-133"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)形式的
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{k}\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由
\begin_inset Formula $E(\boldsymbol{k})$
\end_inset

的表达式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-132"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)可知, 每一个
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{k}$
\end_inset

相应一个能级, 对应于准连续的
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

个
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{k}$
\end_inset

值, 
\begin_inset Formula $E(\boldsymbol{k})$
\end_inset

将形成一个准连续的能带。因此, 以上分析说明, 形成固体时, 原子能级将形成一相应的能带。通常
\begin_inset Formula $E(\boldsymbol{k})$
\end_inset

表达式(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-132"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)还可简化, 考察其中的
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
-J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right)=\varphi_{i}^{*}\left(\xi-\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right)\left[U\left(\xi\right)-V\left(\xi\right)\right]\varphi_{i}\left(\xi\right)d\xi\label{eq:10-134}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}^{*}\left(\xi-\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right)$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{i}\left(\xi\right)$
\end_inset

表示相距为
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{s}$
\end_inset

的两格点上的原子轨道, 积分不为零对应于它们有一定的相互重迭。 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{s}=0$
\end_inset

时, 完全重迭,  这时令
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
J_{0}=\int\left|\varphi_{i}\left(\xi\right)\right|^{2}\left[U\left(\xi\right)-V\left(\xi\right)\right]d\xi\label{eq:10-135}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{s}$
\end_inset

为邻近格点的格矢量时, 应有些重迭, 即(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-134"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式不为零; 当
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{s}$
\end_inset

为较远格点的格矢量时, 重迭较少, 其贡献可略去, 所以一般只保留邻近项, (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-132"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

)式变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
E\left(\boldsymbol{k}\right)=\epsilon_{i}-J_{0}-\sum_{\boldsymbol{R}_{s}=\text{邻近}}J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right)e^{i\boldsymbol{k}\cdot\boldsymbol{R}_{s}}\label{eq:10-136}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
实例
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
作为例子, 下面计算在简单立方晶格中由原子的
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

轨道
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{s}\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

形成的能带。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{s}\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

是球对称的, 在各个方向上重迭的程度相同, 因此在 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-136"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式中
\begin_inset Formula $J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right)$
\end_inset

 有相同的值, 简单表示为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
J_{1}=J\left(\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\right),\qquad(\boldsymbol{R}_{s}\text{为邻近格点的矢径})
\]

\end_inset

而且
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{s}\left(-\boldsymbol{r}\right)=\varphi_{s}\left(\boldsymbol{r}\right)$
\end_inset

, 在(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-134"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 的积分中, 波函数的贡献为正, 故
\begin_inset Formula $J_{1}>0$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
简单立方晶格六个邻近格点的坐标(即邻近格矢
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{s}$
\end_inset

的分量)为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(a,0,0),(0,a,0),(0,0,a),(-a,0,0),(0,-a,0),(0,0,-a)
\]

\end_inset

把这些
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{R}_{s}$
\end_inset

的分量代入(
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:10-136"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

) 式, 得
